text: And there's a beautiful wedding, people.
And what do I see behind a palm tree where I'm hiding?
I see the beautiful wedding cake in a little table
with two chairs for the bride and the groom.
Instead of the bride and the groom,
there is Lupe and Angie sitting perfectly.
And everybody's trying to get the dogs.
And they really are not mean dogs,
but they were faking it really well.
This is what they would do.
They'd like, dog, dog, dog, dog, dog,
eat as fast as they could.
And then they would go, rawr!
